1976;;The Sell Out;;American;;Peter Collinson;;Richard Widmark, Oliver Reed;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Sell_Out_(film);;The CIA, the KGB and the Mossad scheme to eliminate Gabriel Lee, a former CIA agent who defected to the Soviet Bloc but left Eastern Europe to travel to Israel. He seeks his old mentor Sam Lucas for help. Lucas is now running an antiquities store in Jerusalem with his mistress Deborah who was Gabriel's former lover.